#define _SHR_PM_SPEED ( s   ) 
Value:
((16000 == (s)) ? _SHR_PM_16GB : \
                                 (13000 == (s)) ? _SHR_PM_13GB : \
                                 (12000 == (s)) ? _SHR_PM_12GB : \
                                 (10000 == (s)) ? _SHR_PM_10GB : \
                                 (3000  == (s)) ? _SHR_PM_3000MB : \
                                 (2500  == (s)) ? _SHR_PM_2500MB : \
                                 (1000  == (s)) ? _SHR_PM_1000MB : \
                                 (100   == (s)) ? _SHR_PM_100MB : \
                                 (10    == (s)) ? _SHR_PM_10MB : 0)
